r />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkbOFNr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkbOFNr.png&h=6c0725b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsteve寫話捐錢都好信，到時唔捐邊又好似果80萬咁落咗格，好似佢啲卡game咁成年幾都唔發貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且佢都係寫捐612呢d大路，不如自己捐咗佢算<br />\n 味見過邊間黃店咁大口氣用手足價三個字，龍門渣哥做咁多野都唔叫自己良店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要同出邊個價冇分別咁咪即係普通做生意，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用咩鬼手足價<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">水貨化妝品都當黃店咁金鋪都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊度黃啊企開啲啊</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勁多打手即刻咬我話比次機會，啲檔主好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想講咁多黃年宵唔一定要去呢個，唔該大家唔好貪方便，去個藍尸搞既同去咗個政府年宵冇分，政府年宵裏面啲檔主都可以好黃，你會唔會比次機會？</span></span>"},{"pid":"d1887d4646b0af9f9b931155380a6d2ec993a59c","tid":1828310,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T18:53:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bb36497311854c399b0b53bd0bfdb3b1efc973c","tid":1828310,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b055a2ccaefbb8c5941f89a9a7db640f70382a9","tid":1828310,"uid":27349,"like":1,"dislike":224,"score":-223,"citedBy":22,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T16:53:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T18:54:53.000Z","msg":"你全家都會咁樣死"},{"pid":"0187d70e6c93f87cea2af0aa8996392c9e5cc4cf","tid":1828310,"uid":142249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T18:56:45.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"e47ac05085286ae6289c1380dada334b36255e8d","tid":1828310,"uid":142249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b055a2ccaefbb8c5941f89a9a7db640f70382a9","tid":1828310,"uid":27349,"like":1,"dislike":224,"score":-223,"citedBy":22,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T16:53:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T18:57:12.000Z","msg":"係咪心理變態啊 仆街"},{"pid